{"tid":1162794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁君彥：責成秘書處檢視保安安排　政府有權定何時二讀","createTime":"2019-05-20T05:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T06:50:37.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bcd15a7de19d1ba1ed22a3aa5e74f0094ffceef0","tid":1162794,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190520/s00001/449cdce2afe961565355be0b6ad692ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190520%2Fs00001%2F449cdce2afe961565355be0b6ad692ad.jpg&h=1dbc8365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會行管會早上開會討論修訂《逃犯條例》法案委員會會議問題，行管會主席梁君彥會後表示，為了確保大樓使用者安全，行管會將責成秘書處檢視保安安排，稱任何措施都不會收緊傳媒採訪工作。他又說，秘書處會調查及跟進記協和報章投訴，當日採訪期間受阻事件。<br />\n<br />\n至於法案或直接提交大會審議，本身是立法會主席的梁君彥指出，政府有權決定法案何時恢復二讀，不會破壞《議事規則》。他亦舉例稱，回歸前的立法局，亦曾一天內三讀通過法案。<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥另提到，民主派議員區諾軒曾向訪客分發議員助理證件，讓訪客「在不適當地方出現很多次」，行管會向區諾軒發出警告信。"},{"pid":"2c2baeb91f6e812622e6d1a456122c4a3253cd42","tid":1162794,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:25:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190520/s00001/1558329293607/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190520%2Fs00001%2F1558329293607%2F&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ12aNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=ce5dc7bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190520%2Fs00001%2F1558329293607%2F&h=1470a0d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190520/s00001/1558329293607/</a>"},{"pid":"c4640fac8967200e4dfb3489434ee3dfcb43a6c8","tid":1162794,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:25:40.000Z","msg":"屌你一日通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc36ebb866b3e845533cf36b5787f290f357f7a7","tid":1162794,"uid":58031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4640fac8967200e4dfb3489434ee3dfcb43a6c8","tid":1162794,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:25:40.000Z","msg":"屌你一日通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T05:27:32.000Z","msg":"對自己有利就即刻提回歸前"},{"pid":"f85f556b2281bb215b7247c21cfccbe500f2b17a","tid":1162794,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T06:50:37.000Z","msg":"開始收網預備直上大會"}]}